rynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20016/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20016/canvas/1/07742ece-d0d4-46ba-b573-c93e6b6704e3","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T17:05:13.963Z","creator":"Ada ","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>The film ends where it begins: a bathroom. Whereas at the opening of <em>Phantom Thread</em> Reynolds can be seen taking great pains to prepare his body and appearance, he is now laid low by Alma’s poison and craft.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20016/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:42.80203349282296,43.896531100478384,255.1166267942583,165.8971291866029"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20016/canvas/1/4a9dc7a3-503a-4cfa-a3a5-c38bda18f8fa","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T17:05:50.116Z","creator":"Ada ","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Alma promises Reynolds, “I will make you well again.” This recalls Reynolds’s comment <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW49614034 BCX4\" href=\"https://ptannotated.com/items/phan-02950.html\"><u>as he measured her for a dress</u></a> that it is his job as a designer to give her breasts. Through her care of him, she will reshape his body her will as he once promised to do for her.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20016/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:501.91238038277504,173.31190191387557,598.2685406698563,501.6880980861244"}}}]}]}]}